                <h3 class="title is-4">
                    How to use - ASSETS
                </h3>
                <p>
                    You can also link directly to our <strong class="has-text-info">assets</strong> when you need to provide images.
                </p>

                <p>Scheme #1:</p>
                <div class="message">
                    <pre class="message-body">https://assets.epicsevendb.com/<strong class="has-text-info">{:hero|artifact}</strong>/<strong class="has-text-info">{:?_id}</strong>/<strong class="has-text-info">{:?assetType}</strong>.<strong class="has-text-info">{:imageExtension}</strong></pre>
                </div>
                <p>
                    Hero has the following image types:
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong class="has-text-info">full.png</strong> (upper body portrait) - https://assets.epicsevendb.com/hero/bellona/full.png</li>
                        <li><strong class="has-text-info">small.png</strong> (the list image) - https://assets.epicsevendb.com/hero/bellona/icon.png</li>
                        <li><strong class="has-text-info">icon.png</strong> (round face icon) - https://assets.epicsevendb.com/hero/bellona/icon.png</li>
                        <li><strong class="has-text-info">sk_#.png</strong> (the skill icon, where # is the skill slot. If the skill is passive, add a <strong>p</strong> after the number, e.g. sk_2p.png) - https://assets.epicsevendb.com/hero/bellona/sk_2.png</li>
                    </ul>
                </p>
                <p>
                    Artifact has the following image types:
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong class="has-text-info">full.png</strong> (full art) - https://assets.epicsevendb.com/artifact/iron-fan/full.png</li>
                        <li><strong class="has-text-info">small.png</strong> (the list image, always JPG) - https://assets.epicsevendb.com/artifact/iron-fan/small.jpg</li>
                        <li><strong class="has-text-info">icon.png</strong> (round icon) - https://assets.epicsevendb.com/artifact/iron-fan/icon.png</li>
                    </ul>
                </p>

                <p>Scheme #2:</p>
                <div class="message">
                    <pre class="message-body">https://assets.epicsevendb.com/<strong class="has-text-info">{:item|class|attribute|buff|relationship|zodiac-sign}</strong>/<strong class="has-text-info">{:?_id}</strong>.<strong class="has-text-info">{:imageExtension}</strong></pre>
                </div>
                <p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong class="has-text-info">Item</strong> - https://assets.epicsevendb.com/item/dragons-wrath.png</li>
